Corporate finance homework
==========================

This is a homework solution generator for Corporate Finance (Corvinus
University of Budapest).  You may _NOT_ use this to solve your homework
(probably it won't, because homeworks are often differ from each other ;) ) but
it may help you to understand what's going on the business field.

Installation instructions
=========================

The following gems are required to run this (TODO: gemspec):

- builder
- dm-core
- dm-serializer
- do_sqlite3
- haml
- json_pure
- mongrel
- scruffy
- sinatra
- sinatras-hat

